{"tid":85716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啞巴說「新被子好暖和」？ 支媒新聞疑造假","createTime":"2017-01-18T13:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T17:07:27.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93f38a977f52771158b1b47b7178dab69301f372","tid":85716,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phphiZoU1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phphiZoU1.jpg&h=95405860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國四川官媒《內江晚報》在今年1月10日刊登一則新聞，內容敘述一名貧戶收到官方贈送的新被後，滿意地對記者說：「這新被子好暖和，晚上蓋著一定很舒服！」，但下段卻提到這名貧戶是名「啞巴」，引發眾多中國網友質疑是「假新聞」，《新京報》社論更批：「因為是表揚稿，就能讓啞巴說話？」<br />\n<br />\n《內江晚報》該篇報導敘述，在內江市市中區箭道街社區有31戶生活困難戶，他們都收到了官方發送的新棉被、衣物等過冬物資，居民們都相當滿意，有名貧戶趙全貴更滿意地對記者說：「這新被子好暖和，晚上蓋著一定很舒服！」，可是在下一段，記者卻寫說趙全貴是名啞巴，引發議論。<br />\n該篇報導在刊出當下，話題並未發酵，但從昨天開始在中國網路社群引發議論，不少中國網友質疑趙全貴是「怎麼說話的？」連中國媒體也加入批判行列，《新京報》的社論就表示，這類的「表揚性報導」，對媒體來說，重點不是表揚、批評，而是真實、客觀。<br />\n《澎湃新聞》報導，實際聯絡當地居民委員會，值班人員表示，社區確實有這名啞巴貧戶趙全貴，那天他接受採訪時是用紙筆溝通的；《內江晚報》的編輯室人員表示，該則新聞並非假新聞，而是記者編輯責任心缺失，加上相關人員把關不實，正在處理後續，會再向外界公布處理結果。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7cdb9bbd16e33f4743078ec84355389bda160d","tid":85716,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"造假是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7df9eaa5ba21adfce0c95413598ff6d6113ff56","tid":85716,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"偷睇國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d052e2cfceac6354175bff13824bbad62800e52","tid":85716,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"做假都好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9ef0fb9af3194429ca77264b61b0795ffc8d12","tid":85716,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5091edf785d433f698652bf8615ecb729d4d7e8f","tid":85716,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"啞嘅都感動到開聲 感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df26383d1afaf3bdecb5cbbedaa7e6c9488fe7c3","tid":85716,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"這是奇蹟"},{"pid":"15dcd7098851815b8c06ec8cb13f69febaea0fa7","tid":85716,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"有黨既愛護好比耶穌再世 佛光普照<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46991303d211929705ab1047998b71146b4b92f","tid":85716,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}